OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FAt least a thousand officers from the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police and forces around
OL,8,Fthe country are being drafted in to
OL,9,Fpatrol the crowds, with more made
OL,10,Favailable if needed.
OL,12,FMet Assistant Commissioner Ade
OL,13,FAdelekan warned the measures taken by
OL,14,Fpolice cannot "guarantee" disorder
OL,15,Fwill not take place but it is hoped
OL,16,Fthe measures will mitigate disruption.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
