PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FAll protests and counter-protests will
OL,7,Ftake place between Vauxhall and
OL,8,FLambeth bridges and are permitted
OL,9,Fbetween 1pm and 3pm, the Met said.
OL,11,FCounter protesters can assemble on the
OL,12,FMillbank side of the Thames.
OL,14,FLambeth Bridge will be closed, with
OL,15,Faccess only for emergency vehicles.
OL,17,FAssistant Commissioner Adelekan also
OL,18,Fconfirmed the use of the MET's marine
OL,19,Funit on the water.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FThe force needed a "unique plan" to
OL,7,Frespond to "unique circumstances", Mr
OL,8,FAdelekan said but stressed this would
OL,9,Fnot set a precedent.
OL,11,F"I've been in this organisation for 31
OL,12,Fyears, I cannot think of a time when
OL,13,Fwe used it.
OL,15,F"So as far as I'm concerned it's new,
OL,16,Fit's new in my generation of
OL,17,Fpolicing," he said, adding: "It will
OL,18,Fkeep both sides apart whilst also
OL,19,Fallowing people to protest within the
OL,20,Flaw."
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@`O]oD@LOUoD@aO]sD@AOUwD@AOUyD@
OL,26,AJO]yD@]OU|D@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
