PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FMr Adelekan said anticipating protest
OL,7,Fturnout was "not an exact science" but
OL,8,Fthat it was his "professional judgment
OL,9,Fthat numbers I think will go up to
OL,10,F6,000 in terms of the counter protest,
OL,11,Fwhich is a significant number when you
OL,12,Fcombine all of those groups.
OL,14,F"I caveat that by saying you could see
OL,15,Fsignificantly more based on the
OL,16,Fcurrent political situation", later
OL,17,Fadding that police anticipate a
OL,18,F"similar number or more" supporting
OL,19,Fthe protest.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@bO]pD@QOUvD@AOUxD@\O]zD@AOUzD@
OL,26,AXO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
