PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FOfficers are having to be redeployed
OL,7,Ffrom neighbourhood policing to cover
OL,8,Fthe event and patrol Jewish
OL,9,Fneighbourhoods in the capital, Mr
OL,10,FAdelekan said.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood granted
OL,13,Fthe police bid for a month-long ban of
OL,14,Fthe annual march organised by the
OL,15,FIslamic Human Rights Commission
OL,16,F(IHRC), making it the first time such
OL,17,Fa restricting on protest had been
OL,18,Fimposed since 2012.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773846666
OL,3,CMet to use unprecedented Thames
OL,4,Cstrategy ahead of controversial protest
OL,6,FShe told MPs police cannot stop a
OL,7,Fstatic demonstration from taking place
OL,8,Finstead but can dictate its location
OL,9,Fand timing.
OL,11,FShe rejected the suggestion of a
OL,12,Floophole, insisting the challenges
OL,13,Ffaced by police would be "different in
OL,14,Fnature" from a march.
OL,16,FSpeaking in the Commons earlier this
OL,17,Fweek, she warned there is a "greater
OL,18,Fpotential for conflict" at marches for
OL,19,FAl Quds Day because of the ongoing war
OL,20,Fin Iran.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@GO]yD@]OUzD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
